webpackJsonp([0xa19625bea309],{1079:function(t,e){t.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"Why The Swisse Manuka Honey Detoxifying Facial Mask Is A Best-Seller",content:'<p><a href="https://swisse.com/en-au/products/skincare/face/swisse-manuka-honey-detoxifying-facial-mask">The Swisse Manuka Detoxifying Facial Mask</a> is sourced from pure natural ingredients &#8211; and in Australia, we love that. We love it even more if it actually works! And Manuka honey really does.</p>\n<p>A little detail &#8230; Manuka honey is native to New Zealand and is produced by the bees that pollinate the Manuka bush. Topically, this honey is known for its soothing and healing properties and has been used by traditional societies for hundreds of years.</p>\n<p>Over at <a href="https://swisse.com/en-au/home">Swisse</a> they combined this star ingredient with kaolin clay and charcoal, both of which help to <strong>help detoxify skin from impurities and reduce the appearance of large skin pores</strong>,&#8221; says Swisse Technical Manager Innovation, Antoinette-Louise Barnardo.</p>\n<p>Obviously, it&#8217;s a quality product that sells for an awesome price and Australian beauty fanatics know it. Hence the number one in pharmacy status.</p>\n<p>On the topic of masks &#8211; boy are they popular right now. And here&#8217;s why. <strong>Masks are incredibly beneficial</strong> &#8211; and not just for boosting your Instagram feed. You see, masks are intensely soaked in (if they’re of the sheet variety) or made up of (the smooth on type) high levels of active ingredients &#8211; the kind that actually create a change in skin as opposed to just sit on top of it.</p>\n<p>Think<strong> vitamins A, C or niacinamide</strong> for example -all proven anti-agers. Others are based on ingredients such as charcoal (which draws out dirt and grime) or hyaluronic acid (which provides deep moisture).<br />\nGiven that, there are masks out there that can ease sun spots, increase moisture levels, smooth and soften. They can reduce oily patches and minimise the appearance of pores too. And they can do so in just 10 to 15 minutes. Look out!</p>\n<p>The secondary benefit (and it’s a big one), masks force you to take a moment to do nothing. And this <strong>is every bit as beneficial</strong> for your skin (and wellbeing) as the mask itself.</p>\n<p>We recommend you try one today. Go on. Take 10 to 15 minutes for yourself. And gain a beauty benefit or three while you’re at it. Yes, we love the Swisse Manuka version, but if that doesn&#8217;t take your fancy there&#8217;s a swag of others to choose from. Here, a handful of our current faves.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2543 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211020/the-lifting-and-firming-mask-71445-214x300.jpg" alt="" width="214" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211020/the-lifting-and-firming-mask-71445-214x300.jpg 214w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211020/the-lifting-and-firming-mask-71445-768x1077.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211020/the-lifting-and-firming-mask-71445-730x1024.jpg 730w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211020/the-lifting-and-firming-mask-71445.jpg 1050w" sizes="(max-width: 214px) 100vw, 214px" />\n<p><a href="http://www.cremedelamer.com.au/product/9088/30156/masks/the-lifting-and-firming-mask">La Mer The Lifting and Firming Mask, $330</a>. The formula contains La Mer&#8217;s famed nutrient-rich Miracle Broth and the potent Lifting Ferment to visibly tighten and refine the face and neck.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2544 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211109/Even-Better-Brightening-Moisture-Mask-134x300.jpg" alt="" width="134" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211109/Even-Better-Brightening-Moisture-Mask-134x300.jpg 134w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211109/Even-Better-Brightening-Moisture-Mask-768x1719.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211109/Even-Better-Brightening-Moisture-Mask-457x1024.jpg 457w" sizes="(max-width: 134px) 100vw, 134px" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.clinique.com.au/product/1682/30260/skin-care/exfoliatorsmasks/even-better-brightening-moisture-mask">Clinique Even Better Brightening Mask, $52</a>. Formulated to provide intense hydration, leaving skin soft, smooth, supple and radiant.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2545 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211211/sk-ii-facial-treatment-mask-5930-300x256.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="256" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211211/sk-ii-facial-treatment-mask-5930-300x256.jpg 300w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211211/sk-ii-facial-treatment-mask-5930-768x655.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211211/sk-ii-facial-treatment-mask-5930.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="http://shop.davidjones.com.au/djs/en/davidjones/facial-treatment-mask-%286-piece%29">SK-II Facial Treatment Mask, $28 (for one), $150 (for six)</a>. Enriched with Pitera, this deluxe mask deeply hydrates the skin, just like a facial, leaving skin more radiant and crystal clear.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2546 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211302/Skin-Republic-Bubble-Purifying-Charcoal-Face-Mask-1-bd-180x300.jpg" alt="" width="180" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211302/Skin-Republic-Bubble-Purifying-Charcoal-Face-Mask-1-bd-180x300.jpg 180w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211302/Skin-Republic-Bubble-Purifying-Charcoal-Face-Mask-1-bd-768x1278.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211302/Skin-Republic-Bubble-Purifying-Charcoal-Face-Mask-1-bd-615x1024.jpg 615w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211302/Skin-Republic-Bubble-Purifying-Charcoal-Face-Mask-1-bd.jpg 1550w" sizes="(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.theskinrepublic.com.au/product/27013/bubble-purifying-~-charcoal-face-mask">Skin Republic Bubble Purifying + Charcoal Face Mask Sheet, $7.99</a>. When exposed to the air the mask begins to bubble and foam, removing impurities within the skin’s pores.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2547 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211343/Hydrating-Mask-New-241x300.jpg" alt="" width="241" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211343/Hydrating-Mask-New-241x300.jpg 241w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211343/Hydrating-Mask-New-768x956.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211343/Hydrating-Mask-New-823x1024.jpg 823w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08211343/Hydrating-Mask-New.jpg 1038w" sizes="(max-width: 241px) 100vw, 241px" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="https://koraorganics.com/products/hydrating-mask">Kora Organics Hyrdating Mask, $44.95</a>. Contains certified organic noni extract, vitamins, and minerals to refine pores, remove dead skin cells, and promote healthy tissue rejuvenation.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2555 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214109/Aspect-JPG-129x300.jpg" alt="" width="129" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214109/Aspect-JPG-129x300.jpg 129w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214109/Aspect-JPG.jpg 422w" sizes="(max-width: 129px) 100vw, 129px" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.aspectskincare.com/aspect-skin-care-products/probiotic-sleep-mask">Aspect Gold Probiotic Sleep Mask, $59</a>. Apply and leave overnight. Wake to skin that&#8217;s deeply hydrated, calmed and soft.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2557 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214458/Blaq-jpg-168x300.jpg" alt="" width="168" height="300" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214458/Blaq-jpg-168x300.jpg 168w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08214458/Blaq-jpg.jpg 404w" sizes="(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px" />\n<p><a href="http://blaq.co/product/blaq-mask-tube/">Blaq Mask Tube, $29.</a> Activated charcoal to draw out toxins and impurities, this peel-off mask is on its way to becoming a true cult classic.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/08203807/Swisse-JPG.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"skincare",name:"Skincare"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"28980030-0314-54bc-b2b4-03f08243005d"}}}});
